headline: 2 Major Regional Banks to Buy as Industry Prospects Remain Favorable
summary: BNY Mellon and U.S. Bancorp are well-positioned for growth as the Zacks Major Regional Banks industry benefits from restructuring & acquisitions, digitization, modest loan demand and Fed policy shifts.
